{
  "info": {
    "name": "Billing Automation API",
    "_postman_id": "b1a11111-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
    "description": "Coleção de testes da Billing Automation API.\n\nFluxo sugerido (roda de cima pra baixo):\n1. Auth > Register (opcional) ou Login  -> salva {{token}} automaticamente\n2. Clients > Create Client               -> salva {{clientId}}\n3. Invoices > Create Invoice             -> salva {{invoiceId}} e {{gatewayId}}\n4. Invoices > Webhook (PAID)             -> confirma pagamento (usa {{webhookSecret}})\n5. Notifications / LGPD\n\nVariáveis a preencher em Variables (ou num Environment):\n- baseUrl        (default http://localhost:3000 — troque pelo IP da EC2)\n- username/password (login; default admin — casa com AUTH_USERNAME/PASSWORD do .env)\n- webhookSecret  (= WEBHOOK_SECRET do .env, só para o webhook do provider mock)\n\ntoken/clientId/invoiceId/gatewayId são preenchidos automaticamente pelos testes.\n\nDocumentação completa das rotas: postman/GUIA-DE-TESTES.md",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "username", "value": "admin", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "troque-pela-senha-do-.env", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "webhookSecret", "value": "cole-o-WEBHOOK_SECRET-do-.env", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cronSecret", "value": "cole-o-CRON_SECRET-do-.env", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "clientId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "invoiceId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "gatewayId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "subscriptionId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (cria conta + usuário dono)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201 ou 409', () => pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 409);",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (b.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', b.token); console.log('token salvo (register)'); }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"accountName\": \"Minha Empresa\",\n  \"name\": \"Cassio\",\n  \"email\": \"cassio@exemplo.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha-forte-123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Público. Cria um Account (tenant) + User dono e retorna { token, expiresIn }. Retorna 409 se o e-mail já existe."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (emite JWT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.code === 200);",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('tem token', () => !!b.token);",
                  "if (b.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', b.token); console.log('token salvo (login)'); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Público. username = e-mail de um User real OU o AUTH_USERNAME (conta de serviço do .env). Retorna { token, expiresIn }. O token é salvo em {{token}} e usado nas demais rotas (Bearer)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Público. Usado pelo HEALTHCHECK do container e pelo deploy.sh."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Clients",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Client",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.code === 201);",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "const id = b.id || (b.client && b.client.id) || (b.data && b.data.id);",
                  "if (id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('clientId', id); console.log('clientId salvo:', id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Teste\",\n  \"phone\": \"11999998888\",\n  \"document\": \"12345678901\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Cria um cliente no tenant do token. name>=3, phone>=10, document>=11."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Import Clients (bulk upsert)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clients\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Ana Souza\", \"phone\": \"11999990001\", \"document\": \"12345678901\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Bia Lima\", \"phone\": \"11999990002\", \"document\": \"98765432100\", \"status\": \"EM_ATRASO\" }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients/import",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients", "import"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Upsert idempotente por telefone (spec 0008). Reenviar o mesmo lote nao duplica. Retorna { criados, atualizados, ignorados }. Lote de 1 a 1000. status opcional (EM_DIA|EM_ATRASO)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Clients",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Lista os clientes do tenant."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Client by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients/{{clientId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients", "{{clientId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Teste (editado)\",\n  \"phone\": \"11988887777\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients/{{clientId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients", "{{clientId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Campos opcionais: name, phone, document."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/clients/{{clientId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clients", "{{clientId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Invoices",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Invoice (gera cobrança)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.code === 201);",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (b.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('invoiceId', b.id); console.log('invoiceId salvo:', b.id); }",
                  "if (b.gatewayId) { pm.collectionVariables.set('gatewayId', b.gatewayId); console.log('gatewayId salvo:', b.gatewayId); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientId\": \"{{clientId}}\",\n  \"value\": 150.90,\n  \"dueDate\": \"2026-08-01\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Cria a fatura e gera a cobrança no gateway ativo (mock por padrão). Salva invoiceId e gatewayId. value > 0; dueDate em ISO (YYYY-MM-DD)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List All Invoices (paginado, filtro por status)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices?page=1&limit=10&status=PAID",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "10" },
                { "key": "status", "value": "PAID", "description": "opcional: PENDING|PAID|OVERDUE|FAILED" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Lista todas as faturas do tenant, paginado. Filtro opcional ?status=. Status inválido → 400."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Invoice by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/{{invoiceId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices", "{{invoiceId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Busca uma fatura pelo id (útil para ver a que foi paga, já como PAID). 404 se não existir/for de outro tenant."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Overdue/Pending (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/overdue?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices", "overdue"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "10" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Lista faturas pendentes do tenant. 404 quando não há nenhuma."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Webhook: pagamento PAID (mock)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-webhook-secret", "value": "{{webhookSecret}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"gatewayId\": \"{{gatewayId}}\",\n  \"status\": \"PAID\",\n  \"paidAt\": \"2026-07-15T12:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"eventId\": \"evt-teste-001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/webhook",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices", "webhook"]
            },
            "description": "Provider mock: autentica por header x-webhook-secret (= WEBHOOK_SECRET do .env). Corpo: { gatewayId, status, paidAt?, eventId? }. eventId dá idempotência (repetir = duplicate:true). status válidos: PENDING, PAID, OVERDUE, FAILED."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Webhook: idempotência (repetir PAID)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-webhook-secret", "value": "{{webhookSecret}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"gatewayId\": \"{{gatewayId}}\",\n  \"status\": \"PAID\",\n  \"paidAt\": \"2026-07-15T12:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"eventId\": \"evt-teste-001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/webhook",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "invoices", "webhook"]
            },
            "description": "Mesma requisição com o mesmo eventId. Deve responder { success:true, duplicate:true } sem reprocessar (RN-P3)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Subscriptions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Subscription (mensalidade)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.code === 201);",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (b.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('subscriptionId', b.id); console.log('subscriptionId salvo:', b.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientId\": \"{{clientId}}\",\n  \"description\": \"Plano Pro\",\n  \"amount\": 99.90,\n  \"dayOfMonth\": 10\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Cria uma assinatura recorrente (spec 0009). dayOfMonth 1..28 (default 10). startDate opcional. Salva subscriptionId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Subscriptions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Lista as assinaturas do tenant."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Subscription by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions", "{{subscriptionId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. 404 se não existir/for de outro tenant."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Subscription (pausar/retomar/cancelar)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"PAUSED\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions", "{{subscriptionId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Campos opcionais: description, amount, dayOfMonth, status (ACTIVE|PAUSED|CANCELED)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Run generation (n8n)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/run",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions", "run"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Geração recorrente disparada pelo agendador. Gera as faturas das assinaturas ACTIVE vencidas (nextRunDate <= agora). Idempotente por competência. Retorna { processadas, geradas, ignoradas }. Rode 2x: na 2ª as mesmas competências vêm em ignoradas."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Subscription",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "subscriptions", "{{subscriptionId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Remove a assinatura. As faturas já geradas permanecem (FK SET NULL)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Settings",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get payment settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/settings/payment",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "settings", "payment"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Config de pagamento do tenant (spec 0012). Retorna { provider, infinitepayHandle, redirectUrl }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update payment settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"provider\": \"infinitepay\",\n  \"infinitepayHandle\": \"seu-handle\",\n  \"redirectUrl\": null\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/settings/payment",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "settings", "payment"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Define o meio de pagamento DO TENANT. provider: infinitepay|mercadopago|mock. Se infinitepay, infinitepayHandle é obrigatório. A partir daí, as faturas desse tenant usam o recebedor dele."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "System (cron)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Run billing (todos os tenants)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "x-cron-secret", "value": "{{cronSecret}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/system/billing/run",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "system", "billing", "run"]
            },
            "description": "Operação de SISTEMA (cross-tenant, spec 0010). NÃO usa JWT: autentica por header x-cron-secret (= CRON_SECRET do .env). Faz fan-out: enfileira a geração recorrente de TODOS os tenants ativos e responde 202 { enfileirados }. O worker gera as faturas em segundo plano, um tenant por vez. É o que o cron/EventBridge chama diariamente. 401 com segredo errado; 500 se CRON_SECRET não configurado."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Notifications",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Trigger overdue (todas)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/trigger-overdue",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "trigger-overdue"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Enfileira cobranças das faturas vencidas do tenant na fila do RabbitMQ. O worker consome e (com WHATSAPP_PROVIDER=log) apenas loga."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Trigger overdue por invoice",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/trigger-overdue/{{invoiceId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "trigger-overdue", "{{invoiceId}}"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Enfileira a cobrança de uma fatura específica."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "LGPD",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Export client data (portabilidade)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/lgpd/clients/{{clientId}}/export",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "lgpd", "clients", "{{clientId}}", "export"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Exporta os dados do titular (cliente + faturas) para portabilidade (spec 0004)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Anonymize client (direito ao esquecimento)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/lgpd/clients/{{clientId}}/anonymize",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "lgpd", "clients", "{{clientId}}", "anonymize"]
            },
            "description": "JWT. Anonimiza o titular preservando os registros financeiros (retenção legal). Idempotente."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
